title: [Haunted Pass, Dense Trees]
description: A mushroom circle sprouts up in the center of the trail, surrounding a patch of bluegrass.  A group of tall modwirs has a small gap in their branches, offering a little moonlight to seep through the frondescence.  A tall yew dangles a yellowed skull from one of its branches.
